    "Probability flow for probability density function.",
    "The remarkable property of the continuity equation (2.4) is the following: The flow associated with the deterministic ordinary differential equation (2.5) transports the initial distribution µ 0 forward exactly along the density distribution p t of the SDE (2.1).",
